comments: Replay review of the foul called on Mathurin (IND) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Lee (PHX) does not establish a legal position in Mathurin's (IND) path when the body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Lee (PHX) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in Lee's (PHX) path and is firming up as he absorbs the oncoming marginal contact during the screen.
Okogie (PHX) and Turner (IND) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in Okogie's (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Nembhard (IND) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Bridges's (PHX) driving shot attempt.
McConnell (IND) makes contact with the ball last before it goes out of bounds, PHX should've maintained possession of the ball.
Lee (PHX) moves alongside McConnell's (IND) path and maintains a legal guarding position, while absorbing the marginal contact initiated by McConnell during the driving shot attempt.
Nembhard (IND) maintains legal guarding position as Bridges (PHX) initiates the marginal contact that occurs as he rips through. .
Bridges (PHX) is last to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in Wainright's (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
McConell (IND) commits a take foul on Lee (PHX).
Craig (PHX) legally contests Hield's (IND) jump shot attempt.
Mathurin (IND) commits a take foul on Okogie (PHX).
